{"tid":1985632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回流港人被隔離 , 因太肚餓偷吃對面房客午餐","createTime":"2020-04-23T09:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T09:41:52.000Z","uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86a6a165af1f15e3cd641b02c63d95116c6bd71f","tid":1985632,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1522293_1_L_20200423161158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1522293_1_L_20200423161158.jpg&h=d35fb44f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府租用九龍城富豪東方酒店，安排抵港人士到酒店留宿一晚，等候新型肺炎檢測結果，有旅客陸續收到結果，可以離開。<br />\n<br />\n下午2時許，繼續有旅客步出酒店。由加拿大抵港的陳先生非常不滿膳食安排，表示昨晚到酒店吃過一個飯盒，今日上午9時吃了1個牛角包，由中午12時開始，持續打了2小時電話，直至3時許離開都沒獲發午餐，最後<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為太肚餓，把放在對面房門口未有人進食的飯盒吃掉</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n昨日傍晚到酒店，下午2時許離開的徐太說，今日下午獲發1個飯盒，但不滿署方更改取報告時間，而沒有通知留宿人士。徐太說，署方向他們表示中午11時至1時左右會有結果，但到中午未收到通知離開，向酒店服務員查詢後，職員表示不清楚，指有關安排是由政府負責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522293-20200423.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522293-20200423.htm&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6qd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=fe2823b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522293-20200423.htm&h=44781bc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522293-20200423.htm</a>"},{"pid":"44cb38b505bca3fba56ef92d23dfd2598c1c91c5","tid":1985632,"uid":60539,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"因為佢格離房食左佢果個"},{"pid":"3cb702ac722cbeeb73254ecc597e122cc8dd915e","tid":1985632,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"44cb38b505bca3fba56ef92d23dfd2598c1c91c5","tid":1985632,"uid":60539,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"因為佢格離房食左佢果個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70aca404fd5bb024c0682434e37d8cadafda4a6d","tid":1985632,"uid":177590,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44cb38b505bca3fba56ef92d23dfd2598c1c91c5","tid":1985632,"uid":60539,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"因為佢格離房食左佢果個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:41:52.000Z","msg":"屌 好大機會<br />\n去日本浸溫泉，對拖鞋比人著走左<br />\n你又著走返人地果對，dead loop"}]}